						<summary>

						<p>Published in S.I.I. Vol. XIX No. 253</p>						

						<p>This is damaged and built in at the right end. It seems to record a gift of gold by Sōmāsi Sāṉi for burning a perpetual lamp in the temple of Śrī Pōndaip-[perumānaḍigaḷ] at Rājamallachchaturvēdimaṅgalam, besides a land gift.</p>						

